               <provenance>Lǝbsä Qāl and his relatives (wife: Walatta
                     Madḫǝn, father: Tasfā Śǝllāse, mother: Walatta Gabra Manfas Qǝddus, daughter:
                     Walatta Takla Hāymānot) are mentioned in the supplication formulas throughout
                     the Ms. The second part of the name of Lǝbsä Qāl is often overwritten with
                     Krǝstos.</provenance></history>
